Package: heatmap4
Type: Package
Title: Simple Heatmap Function
Version: 0.1.3
Author: Ritu Roy <ritu.roy@ucsf.edu>, Adam Olshen <adam.olshen@ucsf.edu>, Anishka Dhar <anishka.dhar@ucsf.edu> 
Maintainer: Ritu Roy <ritu.roy@ucsf.edu>
Description: A color image of a numerical matrix. A dendrogram can be added to the left side and to the top. This package takes the original heatmap function and reduces the argument complexity.
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: https://github.com/UCSF-CBI/heatmap4/tree/master/heatmap4
